{"tid":1244533,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一個建議俾走唔到資要投資又想參與不合作嘅你","createTime":"2019-06-20T02:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:38:47.000Z","uid":118592,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"99e6ce791e5c508e216d9366c3ccba5de027f41d","tid":1244533,"uid":118592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"好喇其實明白好多人係香港係靠都係靠投資維生<br />\n所以唔可以領晒啲錢呀股票出嚟杯葛香港個市<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係你仲有一個選擇！</span></span></strong>就係將你啲牛牛轉哂落其他非中資嘅證券行！<br />\n有好多隱性中資證券行，就好似富途啲錢用民生銀行，呢間錢行比大陸捉過幾次洗黑錢。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話驚，攞返晒出嚟杯葛中資機構！<br />\n<br />\n富途轉出  <a href=\"https://help.futu5.com/faq/h5-hc-index#/detail/1515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.futu5.com%2Ffaq%2Fh5-hc-index%23%2Fdetail%2F1515&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=23cfd875\" target=\"_blank\">https://help.futu5.com/faq/h5-hc-index#/detail/1515</a><br />\n<br />\nIb轉入 <a href=\"https://ibkr.info/article/65\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibkr.info%2Farticle%2F65&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=9895e71c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ibkr.info/article/65</a><br />\n<br />\n記住無論港股美股乜股都要記得轉！<br />\n<br />\n以下有幾個選擇推介比大家<br />\n<br />\nFirsttrade <a href=\"http://www.firstrade.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.firstrade.com%2F&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=9954f6cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.firstrade.com/</a><br />\nInteractivebrokers <a href=\"https://www.interactivebrokers.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interactivebrokers.com.hk%2F&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=41fc5f62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.interactivebrokers.com.hk/</a><br />\ntd ameritrade <a href=\"https://tdameritrade.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftdameritrade.com.hk%2F&d=ZVysXiw7s3az